org.jruyi.io

Interface CharSequenceCodec.ICharSequenceCodecProvider

  • Enclosing class:
    CharSequenceCodec

    public static interface CharSequenceCodec.ICharSequenceCodecProvider
    This interface defines all the methods that a char sequence codec provider has to implement. It is used to separate the implementation provider from the API module.
